	 	•	Cancellation policies may be superseded by the Guest Refund Policy, safety cancellations, or extenuating circumstances. Please review these exceptions.<br>
	  
	 	•	For a 50% refund, cancellation must be made 30 full days prior to listing's local check in time (or 3:00 PM if not specified) on the day of check in.<br>
	 	•	If the guest cancels less than 30 days in advance, the nights not spent are not refunded.<br>
	 	•	If guest arrives and decides to leave early, the nights not spent are not refunded.<br>

	 Long Term: First month down payment, 30 day notice for lease termination<br>
	 	•	Note: The Long Term cancellation policy applies to all reservations of 28 nights or more.<br>
	 	•	Cleaning fees are always refunded if the guest did not check in.<br>
	 	•	The Stayhappi service fee is non-refundable.<br>
	 	•	If there is a complaint from either party, notice must be given to Stayhappi within 24 hours of check-in.<br>
